Description.Name: Tracer AC/20 Ammo
Description.Details:
Ammo Bins contain the rounds needed for projectile-based weaponry, with at least one bin required per weapon type. Ammo Bins will explode and destroy their installed location when they receive a Critical Hit.

AC/20 Tracer Ammo (Triple) Bins each contain 20 rounds and may feed multiple weapons.

Tracer AC/20 Ammo is +1 Accuracy in low light conditions at the cost of 5 damage.
